WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.566 --> 00:00:02.866
What do you mean?

2
00:00:03.566 --> 00:00:05.100
This is Chen Qianruo's tombstone

3
00:00:05.600 --> 00:00:07.100
He was abandoned by Yuan Kai

4
00:00:07.133 --> 00:00:08.233
Desperate suicide

5
00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:12.466
The Qian Ruo you saw in the nightmare before was him

6
00:00:12.733 --> 00:00:14.500
I just heard about it.

7
00:00:14.500 --> 00:00:16.766
I feel sorry for him and just come to worship

8
00:00:23.000 --> 00:00:25.466
This is Chen Qingru's sister, Chen Qingru.

9
00:00:26.700 --> 00:00:28.733
She used to be Wang Jie of Yuan Group

10
00:00:28.733 --> 00:00:30.166
Get off the road after resigning

11
00:00:33.566 --> 00:00:34.700
Do you know him?

12
00:00:34.700 --> 00:00:37.200
You fake amnesia just to be frugal

13
00:00:37.733 --> 00:00:38.766
Avenge them

14
00:00:39.600 --> 00:00:40.400
Yes

15
00:00:41.366 --> 00:00:41.933
You got it.

16
00:00:41.933 --> 00:00:43.066
I'm not disappointed.

17
00:00:43.500 --> 00:00:45.066
Who are you?

18
00:00:45.066 --> 00:00:46.600
What is your proof?

19
00:00:46.933 --> 00:00:48.633
I'm Chen Qingru's friend.

20
00:00:48.800 --> 00:00:51.400
Approaching you is to kill Yuan Kai to avenge him

21
00:00:51.900 --> 00:00:53.933
It doesn't matter what my name is

22
00:00:53.933 --> 00:00:56.000
You won't even tell me your name

23
00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:57.500
Did you ever love me?

24
00:00:58.900 --> 00:01:01.200
Love built on lies can also be believed

